            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 早前发布了 iOS 及 iPadOS 18.1 Developer Beta 版本，是次更新亦推出了全新 AI 系统 Apple Intelligence。在 Apple Intelligence 人工智能加持下，Siri 将会更加好用，同时 Apple 亦加入了不少处理文字 AI 功能。有兴趣抢先试玩的朋友可以看看小编稍早前和大家分享的教学（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios-18-1-beta-apple-inteligence/tips-2/">教学连结</a>）。今日小编就会和大家看看，Apple Intelligence 有甚么实用的功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253734" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6145412384949386843-694x482.jpg" alt="Apple Intelligence" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6145412384949386843-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6145412384949386843.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>1. 电话即时录音 + 转文字、总结对话内容</h2><p>Apple Intelligence 亦加入了大家期待已久的电话录音功能，可将来电者的说话生成文字稿，结束通话后可在备忘录找到对话录音及文字稿。除此之外 Apple Intelligence 设有「Summary」功能，能够用 AI 总结对话内容，对于工作上时常要讲电话的人来说，这个功能非常实用，可更有条理地纪录和管理电话内容。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254083" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801132051-1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801132051-1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801132051-1-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801132051-1.jpg 807w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲通话状态时可以即时录音</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1254084" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801141227-277x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="1213" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801141227-277x580.jpg 277w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801141227.jpg 381w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲通话结束后可在备忘录找回录音及文字稿</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1254085" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801132127-1-302x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="1112" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801132127-1-302x580.jpg 302w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240801132127-1.jpg 469w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple Intelligence 设有「Summary」功能，可帮用家总结对话内容</p><h2>2. 自由切换打字或语音召唤 Siri</h2><p>以往使用 Siri 时，仅能够在打字和语音二者择一，如果使用打字与 Siri 交流，需要在「辅助设定」选择，每次切换都非常麻烦。升级至 Apple Intelligence 后，用家可以直接点击萤幕底部的白色键，以文字呼唤 Siri，长按电源掣则可与 Siri 以语音对话，毋须再限定一种召唤 Siri 方式。语音召唤 Siri 时，Siri 亦从原来的球体变成框住 4 边的光。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253779" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6145412384949386950-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6145412384949386950-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6145412384949386950.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 可以用文字与 Siri 沟通</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253974" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00104-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00104-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00104.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253975" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00108-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00108-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc00108.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲以语音召唤 Siri 的话，iPad 的四边则会发光</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios-18-1-beta-apple-inteligence/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】香港都可用 Apple Intelligence　安装方法 + 申请教学</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/31/apple-intelligence-privacy-reports/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">确保用户掌握个人资料去向   Apple Intelligence 将提供详细私隐报告</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios18-1-and-ipados18-1-with-apple-intelligence/software/iphone-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Intelligence 功能首次引入   iOS 18.1 和 iPadOS 18.1 Beta 版推出</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>3. 一键总结电邮</h2><p>大家工作时会收到各式各样的电邮，有些电邮非常冗长，如果要全部读完就会浪费很多时间和精神。升级至 Apple Intelligence 后，我们可以将读电邮的工作交由 AI 完成，Apple Intelligence 可以帮我们总结电邮内容。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253783" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/9-2-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/9-2-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/9-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击绿框框住的 Summarize</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253786" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/10-1-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/10-1-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/10-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲随即会在电邮上方显示小总结</p><h2>4. 校对电邮</h2><p>除了总结电邮，Apple Intelligence 亦可帮用家校对，避免寄送文法有错的电邮贻笑大方。打好电邮之后，长按萤幕直至浮现图一所示选项，点击「Writing Tools」即可选择不同写作工具。小编的回复有明显错误，现在就让我们看看 Apple Intelligence 如何帮小编校对电邮。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253883" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图一：选择「Writing Tools」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253885" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_2-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_2-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图二：选择「Proofread」</p><p>Apple Intelligence 会 highlight 有错误的地方并直接修正（红色箭嘴示），绿色框可见目前正使用「Proofread」模式。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253892" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_3-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_3-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图三：Apple Intelligence 会自动修正文法错误</p><h2>5. 改写电邮</h2><p>Apple Intelligence 亦可帮用家利用不同的语气改写电邮。如校对一样，打好电邮之后，长按萤幕直至浮现图一所示选项，点击「Writing Tools」即可选择不同写作工具。这次小编想 Apple Intelligence 帮我用专业的语气改写电邮内容，于是选择了「Professional」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253883" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「Writing Tools」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253896" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_4-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_4-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图二：选择「Professional」（绿色框示）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253900" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_5-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_5-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图三：Apple Intelligence 帮小编将内容改为专业的口吻（见红框），绿框显示目前正在使用「Professional」模式</p><h2>6. 语音备忘录转文字</h2><p>升级至 Apple Intelligence 后，Apple 加入了语音备忘录转文字功能，现在可以将录音转为逐字稿了，录音时亦可即时同步显示语音转文字结果。小编觉得这个功能非常实用，出席记者会、观看发布会时，可以录音并直接转为文字稿，方便之后进行编辑工作，不用再「默书」般边听录音边将句子打出来。小编实测过，利用录音转文字稿功能收听 WWDC 2024，留意到其准确度算高，以后观看发布会就方便得多了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253965" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559887-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559887-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559887.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲录音时可即时同步显示语音转文字结果</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253967" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_10-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_10-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_10.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲录音后亦可翻查文字稿，点击右上角绿色框框住的按钮</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253968" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11-1-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11-1-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_11-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲即可显示逐字稿</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios-18-1-beta-apple-inteligence/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】香港都可用 Apple Intelligence　安装方法 + 申请教学</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/31/apple-intelligence-privacy-reports/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">确保用户掌握个人资料去向   Apple Intelligence 将提供详细私隐报告</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios18-1-and-ipados18-1-with-apple-intelligence/software/iphone-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Intelligence 功能首次引入   iOS 18.1 和 iPadOS 18.1 Beta 版推出</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>7. 总结长文</h2><p>小编每次看见长篇英文文章就会觉得头痛，升级 Apple Intelligence 后，可以利用 AI 帮手「TLDR」以 4 种方式总结文章内容，分别是 Summary、Key Points、List 及 Table。首先 Highlight 你需要的文字，点击「Writing Tools」，选择所需的总结方式即可。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253933" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_8-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_8-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_8.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲highlight 所需文字后点击「Writing Tools」（箭嘴示）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253934" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_9-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_9-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/appleintelligence_9.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲按照个人需要选择不同总结方式</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253935" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559828-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559828-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559828.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Summary 会以一句句子总结选择文字</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253936" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559829-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559829-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559829.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Key Points 以点列式总结选择文字</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253937" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559830-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559830-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559830.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲List 同样会以点列式总结选择文字，但就较 Key Point 更加详细</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253940" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559831-694x482.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="482" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559831-694x482.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/6147911149677559831.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Table 可利用表格总结选取文字，但小编觉得这个功能似乎尚未成熟，生成结果不太实用</p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 120px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;"><strong>总结类型</strong></td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;"><strong>作用</strong></td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Summary</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">以一句句子总结选择文字</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Key Points</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">以点列式总结选择文字</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">List</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">以点列式总结选择文字，但比 Key Points 详细一点</td></tr><tr style="height: 24px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px;">Table</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 24px; text-align: center;">以表格总结选择文字<br />
（现阶段不太稳定，不建议使用）</td></tr></tbody></table><h2>总结：功能实用　惟暂未支援中文</h2><p>小编实际试用过 6 种功能，觉得 Apple Intelligence 对工作上经常要处理文字的朋友非常好用，例如能够帮大家整理文法、改写电邮，亦可以「TLDR」快速摘要长篇文章内容，节省不少时间。作为记者，小编私心最喜欢的功能是录音转文字功能，绝对是出席记者会、发布会的好帮手，大大提升工作效率。惟一要扣分的位置是暂时仍未支援中文，希望 Apple 可以快点推出中文版 Apple Intelligence。</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios-18-1-beta-apple-inteligence/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】香港都可用 Apple Intelligence　安装方法 + 申请教学</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/31/apple-intelligence-privacy-reports/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">确保用户掌握个人资料去向   Apple Intelligence 将提供详细私隐报告</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios18-1-and-ipados18-1-with-apple-intelligence/software/iphone-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Intelligence 功能首次引入   iOS 18.1 和 iPadOS 18.1 Beta 版推出</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/01/apple-intelligence-7-functions/tips-2/">【教学+实试】Apple Intelligence 7 大实用功能　一键校对英文文法 + TLDR 长文总结 + 录音即时转文字</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
